videos.headline: Ragland finds Mayock to put the RedHawks on the board
videos.description: Gus Ragland connects with Luke Mayock for a 24-yard touchdown to give Miami (OH) the lead.

videos.headline: Young's TD extends the RedHawks lead
videos.description: Kenny Young runs for 1-yard into the end zone for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Lewis' TD puts Cincinnati back in the game
videos.description: Hayden Moore connects with Kahlil Lewis for a 20-yard touchdown to close the gap on Miami (OH).
